a top client, they would have had a videotaped public trial in which everyo=
ne would have been encouraged to criticize the departing executive in perso=
nal terms. I suppose the new Bridgewater is gentler, though, plus even in t=
he old Bridgewater they might have been careful about criticizing=C2=A0Dali=
o.
